    "text": [
        "Dear Sir,",
        "I have seen an advertisement in a newspaper regarding a part-time job available  in your hotel. I am writing to inform you  that I am eligible for this vacancy.",
        "I would like to inform you that I have completed my degree in hotel management. Then I have done work in the hotel as a crew member for two years.From One year I was working as an assistant manager in the same hotel. However, the hotel was far away from my residence. Thus, I quit the job last month.",
        "I would greatly appreciate it if you could give detail about the job. I want to know how many hours  I can work in a week and what responsibilities will assign to me.I also want to know whether I need to work at the front desk or I have to work  cleaning rooms.",
        "I would be thankful if the morning shift was available as I do not have a car . In addition, I need  10 minutes break in the afternoon for prayer. If, you have any questions please drop me a message on my number 1333254553.",
        "I am looking forward to hearing from you.",
        "Yours faithfully,",
        "Mark Jones"
